'''Shahir 'Shaz' Chundra''' (yavutse ku ya 27 Gicurasi 1980), ni umukinnyi wa filimi muri  [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika yepfo]] ukomoka mu [[Ubuhinde|Buhinde.]] <ref>https://about.me/shahirc</ref> Azwi cyane kubera uruhare muri serivise za tereviziyo ''Stellenbosch'', ''Abanyamwuga'' ndetse ''n'isi itagaragara'' . <ref name="tvsa">https://www.tvsa.co.za/actors/viewactor.aspx?actorid=8209</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 27 Gicurasi 1980 i Pietermaritzburg, KwaZulu-Natal, [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika y'Epfo]] mu muryango w'Abahinde. <ref>http://www.artistconnection.co.za/controller/artist/65</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Yatangiye gukina afite imyaka 5 nkumukinnyi wumwana. Afite imyaka 17, yatangiye impamyabumenyi yo gukina amafilime muri AFDA, Ishuri ryubukungu bwo guhanga i Johannesburg. Amaze kurangiza, yayoboye ibitaramo byamamaye byurubyiruko muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afrika yepfo]] SABC harimo;''Street Journal'' and ''Kasi 101 and Noted'' . <ref>https://en.notrecinema.com/communaute/stars/stars.php3?staridx=308289</ref> Muri kiriya gihe, yakoze nk'umwanditsi wa sitcoms yo muri Afrika yepfo: ''My Perfect Family'' and ''Majakhatata Records''. . Mu 2011 yimukiye muri [[Amerika]] yiga gukina muri New York Film Academy.

Yabaye umuyobozi muri''Survivor South Africa Champions'' na ''Masterchef Season 3'' . Nyuma yaje kuba Umuyobozi muri  Power Couple South Africa.. Nkumuyobozi wuruhererekane, yakoze progaramu nyinshi zizwi nka ''Reality Check na Bootcamp Msanzi Celebrity Edition'' na ''Zavion Season 1'' . <ref name="tvsa">{{Template:Cite web}}<cite class="citation web cs1" data-ve-ignore="true">[https://www.tvsa.co.za/actors/viewactor.aspx?actorid=8209 "Shahir Chundra"]. tvsa<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">15 November</span> 2020</span>.</cite></ref> Ni n'umucuranzi wakoraga nk'umuririmbyi ukomeye w'itsinda rya rock, 'MadLove', aho yitabiriye inshuro 3 kumurongo wa 1.

Mu 2005, yagaragaye muri filimi ''Isidingo'' aho yakinnye ''nk'umuyobozi Brown'' mu bice bibiri. Igitaramo cyamenyekanye cyane kandi kirakomeza kugeza muri 2012. Yagaragaye kandi  muri serial: ''7de Laan'' na ''Entabeni'' . Muri 2014, yakinnye muri Emmy yegukanye ibihembo mpuzamahanga bya ''Homeland'' season 4, aho yakinnye nka 'Infantry Major' mubice " Krieg Nicht Lieb ". Muri 2017, yakinnye umugome wambere, 'Raj Pillay' muri serial ''Bedford Wives'' yerekanwe kuri SABC 3. Muri uwo mwaka, yakinnye muri filime ''Igikorwa cyo Kwanga'' .

Muri 2018, yagaragaye muri firime yo muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika yepfo]] yibyaha byibasiye ''Mayfair'' . Yakinnye uruhare rwa 'Parvez' muri film, nyuma yaje kwakirwa neza. <ref>https://filmfestival.capetown/mayfair/</ref> <ref>https://m.channel24.co.za/Movies/Reviews/mayfair-20181014</ref> Iyi filime kandi yerekanwe mu iserukiramuco rya Filimi rya 62 rya BFI London na Afurika mu iserukiramuco rya Filime mu Kwakira 2018. <ref>https://www.indianspice.co.za/2018/09/johannesburgs-mayfair-suburb-goes-international-in-new-movie/</ref> <ref>https://www.screenafrica.com/2018/11/06/film/business/mayfair-opens-to-great-reviews/</ref>

Muri 2019, yakinnye muminsi ''3 yo kugenda'' kandi akina 'Roy'. Iyi filime yasohotse mu ikinamico ku ya 25 Mutarama 2019. <ref>https://www.iol.co.za/thepost/3-days-to-go-is-a-crazy-family-drama-18852015</ref> <ref>https://citizen.co.za/lifestyle/your-life-entertainment-your-life/entertainment-movies/2070720/3-days-to-go-review-an-enjoyable-romp/</ref> Muri 2019, yabaye Umuyobozi wuruhererekane kuri televiziyo ''The Bachelor'' .

